  "detailed_description": "Lost Daughter is an open-world action game which tells the story of Sawyer trying to find his daughter.<br><br>Sawyer wakes up in a hospital remembering nothing but he has a daughter. He will go into troubles while searching for his daughter.<br><br><strong>Key Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Open-world<br></li><li>Huge map<br></li><li>Use special powers eating hamburgers, sandwiches and drinking water, coffee and coke<br></li><li>Realistic car controls<br></li><li>Many guns<br></li><li>In-game comics to tell the story<br></li><li>Stalk any character</li></ul>",
